        Creates a security list message in response to the given Security List Request message.

        request - SecurityListRequest message
        securityResponseID - Security response ID
        securityRequestResult - The results returned to a Security Request message

        usePriceDecimals - if price fields should use decimal format

        last - indicates that this is last fragment
        text - optional text, can be null
